ApexComponent.description:
Connect to goinstant by calling `giConnect()`. Passing a room name is optional, if no room is passed will connect to "lobby", Once connected, the event 'GOINSTANT_CONNECTED' is triggered.
Bind functions to event: $(document).bind('GOINSTANT_CONNECTED', fName);
room and connection will be on the window object: window.giRoom window.giConnection
